[This carries echoes of the previous severe epidemic of human & livestock
leptospirosis in Nicaragua. I hope this time we will know which serovars
are involved. While I can guess at why PAHO is correctly playing down
rodent control, maybe one of their people would care to share their
reasons. - Mod.MHJ ................................................mhj/es
